    "DisplayTitle": "Moderate Repairs Needed: Remote Outpost near ~mission(NearbyLocation)",
    "Description": "If you happen to be in the area, please read this.\n\nCitizens for Prosperity is looking for a qualified mechanic to head to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> with the required supplies and perform some repairs.\n\nAs it stands, you\u2019ll need <EM4>six fuses</EM4>, a <EM4>salvaging tool</EM4>, and <EM4>enough RMC canisters to repair five pipes or so.</EM4> That should help us get the outpost functional again. We'll compensate you for your time and materials.\n\nIf you need more information on maintenance work, see <EM4>\u201cCornerstone Developments' Guide to Maintenance\u201d</EM4> entry in your mobiGlas Journal.\n\n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
